I like them alot, but 1 really vital change. Please, make the wings bulkier/thicker than they are rn. The base design looks actually good, they are just too thin. Otherwise, great work, massive upgrade.

Also, idk if its possible, but I would love if you guys would make the white palettes in his gauntlet, Sword and armor a bit darker shade of white than it is rn. It's really bright ingame, and making it just a tad bit darker would make the skin so much more satisfying to use (especially for the Gauntlet's color)

