Hi! Aatrox one-trick here (one-tricktrox). I don't think the skin looks bad in-game tbh, although there are certainly better skins for my boi. However, I noticed his wings during his ult are not centered properly on his back and it's kinda disturbing in a way, especially when moving directly up or down. Another thing about his wings is that they should make his wings bigger and make them flap. These changes would make the skin a lot more appealing.

In addition, if these wings had to be changed because it was reacting very strangely to runes and items, why are the banner wings still the same. It's like the banner wings were fixed, yet the ult wings needed to be changed because they were buggy. My point is that if Riot could fix the banner wings, as they have the same effects and details, then why couldn't they have fixed his ult wings and prevent these strange interactions from runes and items. Hopefully the team that designed the skin will look into this.

